1
00:00:05,711 --> 00:00:08,407
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:12,348
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,418 --> 00:00:16,411
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,755 --> 00:00:19,246
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,325 --> 00:00:23,386
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,462 --> 00:00:27,421
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,901 --> 00:00:33,634
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,340 --> 00:00:37,309
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,745 --> 00:00:41,838
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,581 --> 00:00:43,878
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,216 --> 00:00:46,776
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,827 --> 00:01:00,197
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,399 --> 00:01:01,559
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,634 --> 00:01:05,434
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,771 --> 00:01:10,970
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,243 --> 00:01:12,574
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,645 --> 00:01:14,044
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,113 --> 00:01:20,382
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:30,881 --> 00:01:35,250
Now, let the tenth round begin.

20
00:01:35,819 --> 00:01:37,081
Do your best!

21
00:01:37,454 --> 00:01:38,386
Fatso!

22
00:01:40,858 --> 00:01:41,790
Damn it!

23
00:01:41,859 --> 00:01:43,417
Those two better watch out!

24
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:48,088
I'll end this match quickly and
turn you into mincemeat!

25
00:01:48,832 --> 00:01:50,595
Then let's not play around...

26
00:01:50,667 --> 00:01:53,693
I'll finish you off quickly, Mr. Fatso.

27
00:01:55,139 --> 00:01:58,165
You bandaged cucumber roll!

28
00:01:58,809 --> 00:02:03,746
<i>I know his Achilles heel all too well</i>
<i>from my last battle with him.</i>

29
00:02:04,214 --> 00:02:07,980
<i>Those holes in his arm emit</i>
<i>a pulsing sound, so...</i>

30
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,045
Ninja Art!

31
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,382
Expansion Jutsu!

32
00:02:12,589 --> 00:02:14,716
Followed by the
Hidden Leaf-style Taijutsu!

33
00:02:18,762 --> 00:02:21,060
All I have to do is to prevent him
from aiming at my ears!

34
00:02:21,131 --> 00:02:22,996
Human Boulder Jutsu!

35
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:26,330
Hooray for Big-Boned!

36
00:02:27,438 --> 00:02:28,405
Good!

37
00:02:28,472 --> 00:02:30,963
Squash him, Choji!

38
00:02:31,542 --> 00:02:36,639
<i>This guy can attack sonically without</i>
<i>even touching the opponent...</i>

39
00:02:37,781 --> 00:02:39,942
<i>But that's only when ears are showing!</i>

40
00:02:40,918 --> 00:02:44,012
<i>With Choji's whole head buried,</i>
<i>it's like he's wearing ear plugs.</i>

41
00:02:44,088 --> 00:02:46,249
<i>How does anyone make a sonic attack</i>
<i>on a meat ball,</i>

42
00:02:46,323 --> 00:02:48,484
<i>let alone one that's rolling?</i>

43
00:02:53,263 --> 00:02:55,697
The way you are...
you can barely move, can you?

44
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:57,865
That's where I attack!

45
00:02:58,602 --> 00:03:00,763
It's no use, I'm wearing ear plugs.

46
00:03:00,971 --> 00:03:03,030
No, this is the end!

47
00:03:04,808 --> 00:03:05,570
Oh?!

48
00:03:13,717 --> 00:03:20,088
The human body is made up of 70% water,
and water is able to transmit sound waves.

49
00:03:21,091 --> 00:03:25,755
In other words, your whole body is like
one big ear.

50
00:03:28,932 --> 00:03:31,492
And the winner is, Kinuta Dosu!

51
00:03:34,004 --> 00:03:38,464
<i>Lord Orochimaru...no, Orochimaru!</i>

52
00:03:39,042 --> 00:03:44,070
<i>I'll have you know that...</i>
<i>I'm more than a mere guinea pig.</i>

53
00:03:45,015 --> 00:03:46,346
Are you all right?

54
00:03:46,717 --> 00:03:48,685
I-I want to eat meat...

55
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:51,581
Oh man...
And the guy went easy on him, too.

56
00:03:52,456 --> 00:03:56,256
Although he lost, the least we can
do for him is take him for some BBQ beef.

57
00:03:58,128 --> 00:04:00,494
<i>It's finally over.</i>

58
00:04:01,265 --> 00:04:03,790
<i>At long last, the Final Round...</i>

59
00:04:04,801 --> 00:04:09,397
With this, the preliminaries for
the third exam is completed.

60
00:04:10,174 --> 00:04:16,113
A Shadow in Darkness:
Danger Approaches Sasuke

61
00:04:21,552 --> 00:04:23,884
<i>I wonder what's happened to Naruto?</i>

62
00:04:25,489 --> 00:04:27,616
Let's go outside now.

63
00:04:27,925 --> 00:04:31,326
Iruka Sensei hasn't been alert recently,
so now's our chance.

64
00:04:31,461 --> 00:04:32,393
Hey!

65
00:04:32,563 --> 00:04:33,825
Konohamaru!

66
00:04:34,164 --> 00:04:36,325
You intend to sneak out again, do you?

67
00:04:37,267 --> 00:04:38,529
I-I need to go to the bathroom!

68
00:04:38,602 --> 00:04:39,830
Liar!

69
00:04:41,104 --> 00:04:43,732
To everyone who has advanced to
the Final Round

70
00:04:43,807 --> 00:04:45,741
of the third test of the Chunin Exams,

71
00:04:46,543 --> 00:04:50,001
there's one person who's missing,
but, congratulations.

72
00:04:52,082 --> 00:04:52,878
Sensei...

73
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:53,917
Hmm?

74
00:04:54,751 --> 00:04:56,946
I have a question.

75
00:04:58,722 --> 00:05:00,189
About Sasuke?

76
00:05:01,225 --> 00:05:04,626
Well, I'm sorry, but I don't know much.

77
00:05:05,095 --> 00:05:07,029
But don't worry too much.

78
00:05:08,432 --> 00:05:11,799
<i>From here on, it's up to Sasuke.</i>

79
00:05:14,538 --> 00:05:17,507
Sakura, I have to step out
for a moment.

80
00:05:17,574 --> 00:05:19,565
Please inquire about the
details of the Final Round!

81
00:05:21,111 --> 00:05:21,770
Sure.

82
00:05:25,616 --> 00:05:28,881
<i>Here, in our house,</i>
<i>including Sasuke who's not here,</i>

83
00:05:29,453 --> 00:05:31,216
<i>we have five Leaf,</i>

84
00:05:33,523 --> 00:05:34,854
<i>three Sand,</i>

85
00:05:36,293 --> 00:05:37,988
<i>and one Sound.</i>

86
00:05:39,396 --> 00:05:42,797
Well, I will begin the explanation
of the Final Round.

87
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:45,061
<i>Finally!</i>

88
00:05:52,276 --> 00:05:53,937
The preliminary battles have
ended without incident.

89
00:05:54,378 --> 00:05:55,777
It seems they're now entering
the Final Round.

90
00:05:58,081 --> 00:06:00,072
This land really has become
peaceful, hasn't it?

91
00:06:00,250 --> 00:06:04,516
This peaceful time has put
this country in slumber...

92
00:06:05,756 --> 00:06:10,284
while all the other lands are busy racing
to expand their military.

93
00:06:12,329 --> 00:06:13,887
Would it be possible for us
to take it now?

94
00:06:14,798 --> 00:06:17,062
Humph, I suppose.

95
00:06:17,834 --> 00:06:21,827
Though, I don't know how much fun
it would be to take out that old man.

96
00:06:22,739 --> 00:06:24,206
Is that so?

97
00:06:27,210 --> 00:06:31,806
To me, it looks like you are still having
a hesitation about it.

98
00:06:32,549 --> 00:06:34,847
From now on, the power of
each Hidden Village will clash

99
00:06:34,918 --> 00:06:36,852
with one another in a long
and violent manner.

100
00:06:37,387 --> 00:06:39,252
The Sound village is also one of them...

101
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:43,086
You intend to be the trigger
for all of that...

102
00:06:45,395 --> 00:06:49,058
And use him for a bullet.

103
00:06:49,533 --> 00:06:53,333
Our Sasuke... right?

104
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,929
You guess well.

105
00:06:57,007 --> 00:06:58,702
So well that it's a bit creepy.

106
00:06:59,476 --> 00:07:01,034
Not in the slightest.

107
00:07:01,678 --> 00:07:04,806
I still had no idea about
Dosu, Zaku or Kin.

108
00:07:06,016 --> 00:07:08,780
In gathering information on Sasuke,

109
00:07:08,852 --> 00:07:10,843
I desired to learn their skills

110
00:07:10,921 --> 00:07:14,652
and carried out tactless things like
deliberately subjecting myself to an attack.

111
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,884
You overestimated me.

112
00:07:19,896 --> 00:07:21,261
It seems that you...

113
00:07:21,398 --> 00:07:25,562
you don't trust me completely... yet.

114
00:07:27,037 --> 00:07:30,700
Was it necessary to tell you,
my right hand man,

115
00:07:30,774 --> 00:07:33,004
about the likes of those three?

116
00:07:33,777 --> 00:07:36,268
You see, therein lies
the very proof of my trust.

117
00:07:41,151 --> 00:07:42,243
And because I do...

118
00:07:46,223 --> 00:07:49,021
I would like to leave Sasuke
in your hands.

119
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,391
The Curse Mark that was given to him...

120
00:07:52,829 --> 00:07:55,593
appears to have been sealed by Kakashi.

121
00:07:56,099 --> 00:07:59,193
Though, that won't matter much.

122
00:07:59,436 --> 00:08:02,462
While there is still some
darkness left in his heart...

123
00:08:02,873 --> 00:08:05,137
I want you to abduct him.

124
00:08:06,176 --> 00:08:09,304
That's an uncharacteristically
hasty request, is it not?

125
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,971
There's a little something troubling me...

126
00:08:14,851 --> 00:08:16,546
Is it Naruto Uzumaki?

127
00:08:19,089 --> 00:08:22,058
<i>You're quite a sharp one,</i>
<i>aren't you?</i>

128
00:08:23,260 --> 00:08:28,425
Sasuke has lived for revenge
against his older brother Itachi,

129
00:08:29,266 --> 00:08:32,429
and will not rest until he
has achieved that aim.

130
00:08:33,236 --> 00:08:35,500
Nevertheless, in battle with me,

131
00:08:35,572 --> 00:08:38,166
he was aware that there were things
beyond his power and

132
00:08:38,241 --> 00:08:40,300
faced death without fear.

133
00:08:40,644 --> 00:08:43,738
I didn't think he'd be the type of
person who would be in a hurry to die.

134
00:08:44,681 --> 00:08:46,376
According to your information,

135
00:08:46,450 --> 00:08:52,878
contact with that Nine Tailed kid has
altered Sasuke's heart and mind.

136
00:08:53,590 --> 00:08:57,526
So much so, that he possesses
some influence over Sasuke.

137
00:08:58,428 --> 00:09:01,556
The best thing to do is to get Sasuke
away from him immediately...

138
00:09:02,699 --> 00:09:07,159
And quickly turn him in my color.

139
00:09:15,979 --> 00:09:16,843
Well, then...

140
00:09:17,013 --> 00:09:17,877
Kabuto...

141
00:09:18,014 --> 00:09:19,072
You...

142
00:09:21,451 --> 00:09:23,646
If you wish to stop me...

143
00:09:31,261 --> 00:09:34,992
You have no choice
but to kill young Sasuke, now.

144
00:09:36,833 --> 00:09:39,597
You can't possibly kill me...

145
00:09:39,903 --> 00:09:44,169
Though you are strong, you're only
in the same league as Kakashi.

146
00:09:55,452 --> 00:09:56,544
Just kidding...

147
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,787
Now, run along

148
00:09:58,955 --> 00:10:01,287
I trust you.

149
00:10:08,398 --> 00:10:10,161
<i>That face...</i>

150
00:10:10,567 --> 00:10:12,626
<i>I wonder what could possibly</i>
<i>be going on in his head?</i>

151
00:10:13,837 --> 00:10:15,566
The Final Round is where
each one of you

152
00:10:15,639 --> 00:10:18,005
will show off your battle skills
in front of everyone.

153
00:10:18,408 --> 00:10:21,206
I want you to satisfactorily demonstrate
and show off your ability

154
00:10:21,278 --> 00:10:24,679
as representative battle forces
of your respective lands.

155
00:10:25,348 --> 00:10:28,943
Accordingly, the Final Round will
commence one month from now.

156
00:10:29,553 --> 00:10:31,851
W-We're not going to
do it here, right now?

157
00:10:32,322 --> 00:10:35,450
This is so that there's
a suitable period of preparation.

158
00:10:36,126 --> 00:10:37,423
What do you mean?

159
00:10:38,061 --> 00:10:39,323
That is to say...

160
00:10:39,429 --> 00:10:41,989
Along with the announcement of
the conclusion

161
00:10:42,065 --> 00:10:44,829
of the preliminary match to each
country's Daimyo and Shinobi leaders,

162
00:10:44,901 --> 00:10:48,701
readying the summons for
Final Round requires preparation time...

163
00:10:48,772 --> 00:10:54,267
not to mention the time it takes
for you examinees to prepare.

164
00:10:54,411 --> 00:10:57,574
<i>This old man always has such</i>
<i>a roundabout way of saying things.</i>

165
00:10:57,814 --> 00:11:00,078
I don't quite get what
you're trying to say.

166
00:11:00,183 --> 00:11:01,411
What do you mean?

167
00:11:02,185 --> 00:11:04,210
In other words,
in order to know your adversary,

168
00:11:04,287 --> 00:11:06,255
in order to prepare yourself,
time is necessary.

169
00:11:06,590 --> 00:11:09,525
Time to analyze what you learned about
the adversaries in the preliminaries...

170
00:11:09,593 --> 00:11:12,084
time to take stock of your successes.

171
00:11:12,295 --> 00:11:14,923
The battles until now were
like actual battles

172
00:11:14,998 --> 00:11:19,560
it presupposed situations in which
you can't know your adversary.

173
00:11:20,203 --> 00:11:21,670
<i>That's for sure...</i>

174
00:11:21,738 --> 00:11:25,174
<i>I never dreamed that this guy</i>
<i>could make sand into a weapon.</i>

175
00:11:26,076 --> 00:11:28,601
However, this is not the case
in the Final Round.

176
00:11:28,979 --> 00:11:33,973
Some of you might have already
revealed everything in front of your rivals...

177
00:11:35,085 --> 00:11:37,246
In the spirit of fairness and equality,

178
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:41,757
you will have a month to
train yourself to further your skills.

179
00:11:55,472 --> 00:11:57,337
<i>Now, I can't be thinking of this</i>

180
00:11:57,407 --> 00:11:59,967
<i>as some sort of month long</i>
<i>holiday and do nothing! Believe it!</i>

181
00:12:00,377 --> 00:12:02,242
<i>Seriously! Seriously!</i>

182
00:12:14,669 --> 00:12:17,137
It might not be good idea to
excel too much, is it?

183
00:12:17,805 --> 00:12:22,401
We failed to stay out of Orochimaru's
watchful eye,

184
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:24,200
and it was unfortunate for us both.

185
00:12:25,146 --> 00:12:28,809
<i>Under this gentle exterior,</i>
<i>a seed of evil took root</i> -

186
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:30,915
<i>and it was this seed that was exploited...</i>

187
00:12:31,586 --> 00:12:33,451
<i>Some day, through that Ninjutsu...</i>

188
00:12:34,522 --> 00:12:35,648
<i>this child will as well...</i>

189
00:12:41,596 --> 00:12:42,585
Kabuto...

190
00:12:43,331 --> 00:12:44,821
Who knows?

191
00:12:45,099 --> 00:12:47,897
Perhaps he really will kill Sasuke.

192
00:13:03,184 --> 00:13:04,913
I have to give it you, Kakashi...

193
00:13:05,853 --> 00:13:08,378
Stopping my attack from your blind spot...

194
00:13:09,290 --> 00:13:14,421
But, you'd better ready at least
10 of your men next time.

195
00:13:18,132 --> 00:13:21,431
<i>The Anbu that I prepared were</i>
<i>taken out without difficulty...</i>

196
00:13:22,637 --> 00:13:25,162
You're not an ordinary Genin are you?

197
00:13:25,873 --> 00:13:29,400
You caught a whiff of me and immediately
readied your weapon...

198
00:13:29,477 --> 00:13:30,910
you're quite impressive.

199
00:13:31,312 --> 00:13:33,337
No, I'm not all that.

200
00:13:34,215 --> 00:13:35,614
What do you want with Sasuke?

201
00:13:36,084 --> 00:13:38,780
Depending on circumstances,
I'll haul you off to questioning.

202
00:13:40,254 --> 00:13:43,781
I wonder if that's possible
for the likes of you...

203
00:13:44,926 --> 00:13:47,292
Are you looking to take me on?

204
00:13:51,599 --> 00:13:55,228
You are the son of the chief of the
Leaf medical corps, aren't you?

205
00:13:56,270 --> 00:13:59,865
Your name, was it, Kabuto Yakushi?

206
00:14:01,876 --> 00:14:04,071
Are you affiliated with Orochimaru?

207
00:14:06,114 --> 00:14:08,207
If you arrest me here now,

208
00:14:08,683 --> 00:14:11,709
you might never be able to prove
my connection to Orochimaru.

209
00:14:12,153 --> 00:14:14,621
Shut up and confine your answers
to my questions.

210
00:14:15,289 --> 00:14:16,688
What if I say "No"?

211
00:14:17,625 --> 00:14:19,752
I'm the one asking the
questions around here.

212
00:14:20,261 --> 00:14:21,660
Now give me some answers.

213
00:14:21,863 --> 00:14:24,730
You'll find out before long anyway
if you let me go,

214
00:14:25,666 --> 00:14:28,100
so can you make an exception
just this once?

215
00:14:28,503 --> 00:14:31,472
You, willful little brat...

216
00:14:32,874 --> 00:14:34,774
Don't mess around with grown-ups.

217
00:14:35,510 --> 00:14:38,274
Don't be so arrogant.

218
00:14:39,046 --> 00:14:41,571
The circumstances are in my favor...

219
00:15:08,776 --> 00:15:10,004
<i>I should have known.</i>

220
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,447
<i>A shadow clone!</i>

221
00:15:41,943 --> 00:15:43,308
Darn... I've let him escape.

222
00:15:49,517 --> 00:15:50,711
Impressive...

223
00:15:56,090 --> 00:15:56,988
<i>As I suspected...</i>

224
00:15:57,625 --> 00:15:58,853
<i>This is the Dead Soul Jutsu,</i>

225
00:15:58,926 --> 00:16:01,861
<i>where one temporarily animates</i>
<i>and controls the heart of a dead body.</i>

226
00:16:03,030 --> 00:16:05,430
<i>Meticulously transforming even the face...</i>

227
00:16:06,601 --> 00:16:10,765
<i>and also stopping his heartbeats</i>
<i>and eliminating all traces of his body odor...</i>

228
00:16:10,938 --> 00:16:15,671
<i>in order to prepare an escape by</i>
<i>impersonating a murdered Anbu...</i>

229
00:16:17,445 --> 00:16:20,812
<i>He wasn't raised as the adopted son of</i>
<i>the chief of the medical corps for nothing.</i>

230
00:16:21,916 --> 00:16:24,680
<i>If someone this good is working</i>
<i>for Orochimaru...</i>

231
00:16:26,287 --> 00:16:27,948
<i>I can't stay as I am now...</i>

232
00:16:30,091 --> 00:16:31,683
Now that that's done...

233
00:16:31,759 --> 00:16:34,990
I'd like to let you take your leave...

234
00:16:35,263 --> 00:16:37,527
But first, for the Final Round,

235
00:16:37,598 --> 00:16:40,931
there is one more important
matter to take care of.

236
00:16:41,102 --> 00:16:45,300
Let's get on with it,
so we can get to training

237
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:49,542
Now, now. I want you all to
calmly take one slip of paper

238
00:16:49,610 --> 00:16:52,078
from the box that Anko is holding.

239
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:57,645
I'm going to go around in order...
take only one.

240
00:17:06,494 --> 00:17:08,121
Good, everyone has taken
a number.

241
00:17:08,429 --> 00:17:12,024
Then, from left to right, tell me
the number on your slip of paper.

242
00:17:12,600 --> 00:17:13,498
I'm eight.

243
00:17:14,602 --> 00:17:15,762
I'm one.

244
00:17:16,304 --> 00:17:17,032
Seven.

245
00:17:17,638 --> 00:17:18,400
Five.

246
00:17:19,006 --> 00:17:19,734
Three.

247
00:17:19,974 --> 00:17:20,736
Nine.

248
00:17:20,875 --> 00:17:21,500
Two.

249
00:17:21,642 --> 00:17:22,438
Six.

250
00:17:23,010 --> 00:17:25,774
In other words, he has number four.

251
00:17:26,414 --> 00:17:27,073
Uh huh.

252
00:17:28,049 --> 00:17:29,812
Very well, I will tell you

253
00:17:29,884 --> 00:17:32,910
about how the Final Round
tournament will work!

254
00:17:33,854 --> 00:17:35,321
Huh?

255
00:17:35,389 --> 00:17:37,323
Is that what these
drawing lots were for?

256
00:17:37,792 --> 00:17:40,659
Ibiki, bring forth the pairings.

257
00:17:40,895 --> 00:17:41,691
Yes, sir.

258
00:17:49,437 --> 00:17:50,597
<i>He's so far away.</i>

259
00:17:51,205 --> 00:17:54,072
<i>Is that all the Final Round is,</i>
<i>a tournament?</i>

260
00:17:54,775 --> 00:17:56,868
<i>Shoot! I have one extra round.</i>

261
00:17:57,445 --> 00:18:00,414
<i>Vendetta for Choji?</i>
<i>Give me a break!</i>

262
00:18:02,483 --> 00:18:05,077
<i>I'm so relieved to know that</i>
<i>I won't be in the same section as Gaara.</i>

263
00:18:05,519 --> 00:18:07,180
<i>Sasuke Uchiha...</i>

264
00:18:08,122 --> 00:18:09,316
<i>Perfect.</i>

265
00:18:10,257 --> 00:18:13,317
<i>Hyuga Neji, right off the bat?</i>

266
00:18:14,562 --> 00:18:16,530
<i>This couldn't be better!</i>
<i>Believe it!</i>

267
00:18:18,199 --> 00:18:20,633
<i>Sasuke has to go up against him...?</i>

268
00:18:25,573 --> 00:18:26,972
Could I ask a question?

269
00:18:27,308 --> 00:18:28,104
Go ahead.

270
00:18:28,376 --> 00:18:32,608
Does this mean that there will
only be one winner of the tournament?

271
00:18:32,913 --> 00:18:37,213
That only one of us will be
able to become a Chunin?

272
00:18:37,752 --> 00:18:39,583
No, on the contrary.

273
00:18:39,954 --> 00:18:43,321
The judges of the Final Round,
of which I am one,

274
00:18:43,391 --> 00:18:44,722
will be made up of the Kazekage,

275
00:18:44,792 --> 00:18:47,556
the Daimyo from various countries
who will assign you your missions,

276
00:18:47,628 --> 00:18:50,620
and the Shinobi Leaders.

277
00:18:51,065 --> 00:18:52,794
Through this tournament,

278
00:18:52,867 --> 00:18:57,099
these judges will be able to make
a thorough evaluation,

279
00:18:57,171 --> 00:18:59,264
and come to a decision as to
whether each one of you

280
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:02,173
possesses the qualities incumbent
of a Chunin.

281
00:19:02,309 --> 00:19:07,076
Even if someone loses the first round,
they can still become a Chunin.

282
00:19:07,415 --> 00:19:12,250
So there's a chance that all
of us will become Chunin?

283
00:19:12,853 --> 00:19:17,290
Correct, but conversely,
there's also a chance that none of you will.

284
00:19:17,792 --> 00:19:20,556
To "advance" in the tournament,

285
00:19:20,928 --> 00:19:25,331
means maximizing chances
to appeal yourselves to the judges.

286
00:19:25,933 --> 00:19:28,265
Understood, Shikamaru?

287
00:19:29,336 --> 00:19:32,533
<i>This is all a real pain in my...</i>

288
00:19:33,207 --> 00:19:35,141
Thank you for your patience.

289
00:19:35,309 --> 00:19:37,436
We will adjourn until next month.

290
00:19:37,845 --> 00:19:40,871
<i>The second round will either be</i>
<i>No Eyebrows from Sand or Sasuke, huh?</i>

291
00:19:42,249 --> 00:19:44,581
<i>That guy is so strong he kicked</i>
<i>Bushy Brow's butt.</i>

292
00:19:45,052 --> 00:19:46,679
<i>Sand Coffin!</i>

293
00:19:53,661 --> 00:19:56,186
<i>I want to fight you, too.</i>

294
00:20:02,470 --> 00:20:04,495
<i>Now that it's come to this,</i>
<i>I've got to see Kakashi Sensei.</i>

295
00:20:04,939 --> 00:20:08,238
Umm, where's the room
that Sasuke's in?

296
00:20:08,309 --> 00:20:10,743
I'm sorry. Mr. Sasuke
is not allowed visitors.

297
00:20:10,811 --> 00:20:13,302
What?! Hey, hey!
What's up with that?!

298
00:20:13,447 --> 00:20:14,880
I'm sorry, those are the rules.

299
00:20:15,015 --> 00:20:16,414
Why, Sis, tell me why?

300
00:20:16,484 --> 00:20:19,248
Naruto, this is a hospital.
Keep it down.

301
00:20:20,454 --> 00:20:21,546
Kakashi Sensei!

302
00:20:22,056 --> 00:20:22,920
Say! Say!

303
00:20:23,657 --> 00:20:25,352
I've got a favor to ask!

304
00:20:25,426 --> 00:20:26,893
You don't need to say it all.

305
00:20:27,628 --> 00:20:29,289
Well, I thought it would
come to this so...

306
00:20:29,630 --> 00:20:32,565
I searched for someone
to watch your training.

307
00:20:32,867 --> 00:20:36,234
Why?! I want you to, Kakashi Sensei!

308
00:20:36,504 --> 00:20:38,597
I have some matters to take care of.

309
00:20:38,873 --> 00:20:41,137
I don't have the time to trouble
myself with you.

310
00:20:43,544 --> 00:20:45,535
Oh! Aha...!

311
00:20:46,380 --> 00:20:48,940
You're going to train
Sasuke, aren't you!

312
00:20:49,183 --> 00:20:50,582
Well, don't say that.

313
00:20:51,218 --> 00:20:54,381
I found a sensei who's
more reliable than I am!

314
00:20:54,455 --> 00:20:56,320
Well... who is it?

315
00:20:57,191 --> 00:20:58,055
It's me!

316
00:20:58,459 --> 00:20:59,084
Huh?

317
00:21:01,295 --> 00:21:02,159
You!

318
00:21:02,229 --> 00:21:04,094
The Closet Perv!

319
00:21:04,231 --> 00:21:05,391
Such insolence!

320
00:21:06,711 --> 00:21:11,171
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

321
00:21:11,315 --> 00:21:19,654
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

322
00:21:20,658 --> 00:21:29,327
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

323
00:21:29,734 --> 00:21:37,573
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

324
00:21:38,843 --> 00:21:44,247
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

325
00:21:44,315 --> 00:21:48,342
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

326
00:21:48,419 --> 00:21:51,980
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

327
00:21:52,323 --> 00:22:00,856
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

328
00:22:01,132 --> 00:22:06,331
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

329
00:22:06,404 --> 00:22:10,807
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

330
00:22:10,875 --> 00:22:14,641
<i>Just sing.</i>

331
00:22:14,879 --> 00:22:20,044
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

332
00:22:20,117 --> 00:22:22,312
<i>The two are one</i>

333
00:22:22,420 --> 00:22:28,689
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

334
00:22:29,193 --> 00:22:34,290
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

335
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:41,166
Damn! I'm not satisfied with this!

336
00:22:41,403 --> 00:22:43,268
I don't care if you're elite tutor
or whatever,

337
00:22:43,338 --> 00:22:45,499
but there's no way
I'm not going to get stronger

338
00:22:45,574 --> 00:22:47,633
if I'm to learn from the Closet Perve
weaker than me!

339
00:22:47,776 --> 00:22:50,939
I have to get strong by any
means necessary, no matter what!

340
00:22:51,413 --> 00:22:53,472
If you're really a strong ninja,

341
00:22:53,582 --> 00:22:56,745
just try to convince me
with your sheer strength!

342
00:22:57,185 --> 00:23:01,781
Next episode: "Ebisu Returns:
Naruto's Toughest Training Yet!"

343
00:23:02,123 --> 00:23:04,284
I'm gonna win this time around, too!
